Scenario name : Success Create Equipment Inspection Form

No.      Test Step                                           Expected results
1.       Open the Equipment Inspection menu                  The Equipment Inspection page displays list of previous submissions
2.       Tap the New Submission button                       App opens the Equipment Inspection form page
3.       App requests form schema from server                Dynamic form fields are loaded based on the form code
4.       Form Code field displayed                           Form Code appears correctly on top of the form
5.       Input text fields (if available)                    Text fields accept input with no issues
6.	     Select date from Date Picker	                       Date picker opens and selected date appears in the field
7.	     Open dropdown/select fields	                       Dropdown shows correct options and user can select 1 option
8.	     Tap radio button options	                           Only one radio option can be selected at a time
9.	     Tap Image Picker field	                             Camera/Gallery opens successfully
10.	     Choose or capture an image	                         Image preview appears in the field
11.	     Fill all required fields	                           Required fields show validation if left empty
12.	     Submit the form	                                   App validates all fields, no errors shown
13.	     App sends submission to server	                     API request is successful, form is stored
14	     Redirected back to submission list	                 Newly submitted form appears in the list with correct timestamp
15	     Close and reopen the app	                           All previously submitted data is still available and loaded correctly


Scenario name : Check max field of Inspection Form

No.     Test Step                                            Expected results
1.       Open the Equipment Inspection menu	                 The Equipment Inspection page displays list of previous submissions
2.       Tap the New Submission button	                     App opens the Equipment Inspection form page
3.       App requests form schema from server	               Dynamic form fields are loaded based on the form code
4.       Form Code field displayed	                         Form Code appears correctly on top of the form
5.       Input field up to max of 50 fields                  Cannot add any more fields
6.	     Submit the form	                                   App validates all fields, no errors shown
7.	     App sends submission to server	                     API request is successful, form is stored
8.       Redirected back to submission list	                 Newly submitted form appears in the list with correct timestamp
9.	     Close and reopen the app	                           All previously submitted data is still available and loaded correctly
